 1→//! COR24 CPU emulator
 2→//!
 3→//! The COR24 is a C-Oriented RISC 24-bit architecture with:
 4→//! - 3 general-purpose 24-bit registers (r0, r1, r2)
 5→//! - 5 special registers: fp=r3, sp=r4, z=r5, iv=r6, ir=r7
 6→//! - Single condition flag (C)
 7→//! - Variable-length instructions (1, 2, or 4 bytes)
 8→//! - 16MB address space (24-bit)
 9→//! - Little-endian byte ordering
10→
